Winston for Reddit

This is the official repository for Winston, a beautiful, FOSS, native handcrafted Reddit client for iOS.

This is a WIP, both the app and this README.

You can join the TestFlight here: https://testflight.apple.com/join/3UF8bAUN

You can support this project by subscribing to our Patreon: https://patreon.com/user?u=93745105
